"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-break-dancing-olympic-games-paris-2024-b1169821.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Breakdancinghas attracted considerable interest since it was first announced to be added to this year's programme as a newsportfor theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Its debut follows the outstanding success of the sport in the 2018 Summer Youth Olympic Games in Buenos Aires.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999999998995008, \"rank\": 5.64665425954502e-11, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A fusion of acrobatic movements and stylised footwork, with a key role played by the DJ and MC during battles, breaking is an urbandancestyle from America.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9999635953682696, \"rank\": 3.6405957159947406e-05, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It originated in the 1970s and by the 1990s, international competitions for breaking were being held, popularising the dance style and attracting global interest.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this year, will be the first time thedanceis whirled into theOlympics.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As millions of worldwide viewers tune in to watch the games live, here's what to expect from breaking to bring you up to speed:  The breaking competition comprises two events - one for men and one for women - where 16 B-Boys and 16 B-Girls will face off in solo battles.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hottest hotel openings for 2026  Yorke Dance Project: Modern Milestones review - lean, muscular modern dance  NBA London 2026 LIVE: Memphis Grizzlies vs Orlando Magic come to the UK  Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter  Athletes will use a combination of power moves such as windmills, the 6-step, and freezes as they adapt their style and improvise to the beat of the DJ's tracks in a bid to secure the judges' votes and take home the first Olympic breaking medals.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999928103833712, \"rank\": 7.183753787089977e-06, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999623728406, \"rank\": 3.762503035694068e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\", \"score\": 0.9999999997103259, \"rank\": 2.8954159441633674e-10, \"text\": \"Memphis Grizzlies\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9657533972996466, \"rank\": 0.03545987218619905, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9999635953682696, \"rank\": 3.6405957159947406e-05, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitors are judged on six criteria, including creativity, personality, technique, versatility, performance, skills and musicality.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The current schedule shows competitions over two days in August.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The following UK times show when each phase will be held.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9657533972996466, \"rank\": 0.03545987218619905, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"09 August:  15:00 B-Girls Round Robin  19:00 B-Girls Quarterfinal 1  19:07 B-Girls Quarterfinal 2  19:14 B-Girls Quarterfinal 3  19:21 B-Girls Quarterfinal 4  19:45 B-Girls Semifinal 1  19:52 B-Girls Semifinal 2  20:14 B-Girls Bronze Medal Battle  20:23 B-Girls Gold Medal Battle  10 August:  15:00 B-Boys Round Robin  19:00 B-Boys Quarterfinal 1  19:07 B-Boys Quarterfinal 2  19:14 B-Boys Quarterfinal 3  19:21 B-Boys Quarterfinal 4  19:45 B-Boys Semifinal 1  19:52 B-Boys Semifinal 2  20:14 B-Boys Bronze Medal Battle  20:23 B-Boys Gold Medal Battle  London is to host a week-long exhibition inMarble Archto celebrate the sport's inclusion in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999623728406, \"rank\": 3.762503035694068e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marble Arch London BID are hosting demonstrations between 12.30pm to 1.30pm and have arranged for breakers Breakmission 3x3s Shahii, Chris and Chuckz - also members of the award-winning breakdancing group the Gully LDN Squad - to perform.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The exhibition, Breaking Marble Arch will run from Monday, July 15 to Friday, July 19 and will take place adjacent to the Marble Arch monument.\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kay Buxton, Chief Executive, Marble Arch London BID, said:\\u00a0\\\"We are really excited to be hosting Breaking Marble Arch as we build up to the Olympic Games inParis.\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2970, \"end\": 2976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buxton_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.7117961039138825, \"rank\": 0.4048967035660567, \"text\": \"Buxton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buxton_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buxton_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2995, \"end\": 3006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marble_Arch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.742907151382306e-16, \"text\": \"Marble Arch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marble_Arch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marble_Arch\"}, {\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999623728406, \"rank\": 3.762503035694068e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_improvement_district\", \"score\": 0.9999999855299394, \"rank\": 1.4470224928948576e-08, \"text\": \"BID\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_improvement_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_improvement_district\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking is a fantastic sport which combines multiple disciplines and can be done by anyone anywhere.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are looking forward to welcoming Shahii, Chris and Chuckz to Marble Arch as they showcase some of the moves which will be on show in Paris.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3368, \"end\": 3373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2243898466491617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We encourage the whole community to come and see the talented trio in action.\\\"\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris Arias from Gully LDN Squad, said: \\\"Gully LDN is excited to welcome a new audience to our scene, especially with breaking now being part of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3478, \"end\": 3481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Majors\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.6929174838609965e-19, \"text\": \"LDN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Majors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Majors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We aim to showcase how breaking has positively shaped us both physically and mentally.\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join us in celebrating this dynamic sport and experience its transformative benefits.\\\"\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 4667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3849, \"end\": 3858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999037772842, \"rank\": 6.771310011539623e-08, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedi